quote.summary: Beijing 51WORLD Digital Twin Technology Co Ltd is a China-based company primarily engaged in the sale of digital twin related software platform and provision of related services. The Company mainly offer products and solutions under three businesses. 51Aes is a digital twin development and application platform designed to enhance enterprise customer design and operational efficiency, supporting the transformation of digital intelligence across various industries. 51Sim is a synthetic data and simulation platform The core products include SimOne, a simulation platform for intelligent driving and robotics, DataOne, a data closed-loop and synthetic data platform, and TIM, a traffic information modeling platform. 51Earth aims to create a digital twin world that is accessible to and contributable by both enterprises and consumers. The Company primarily conducts its businesses in domestic market.
